    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0

    v1 = (((v1 + 0.36 * tmp + 0.87) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.21)) + wp.exp((tmp + 0.60 * v0 + 0.20)))
    tmp = v2
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.37)))
    v1 = wp.abs(v0)
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos((v1 + 0.29 - tmp + 0.18)))
    tmp = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.90 / tmp + 0.92)) - ((v1 + 0.26 * v2 + 0.46) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.89)))
    data[tid] = v0
